{
  "stem": "11175.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My mother, according to her telling me, it is at this and this time you were born, this and this month you were born, it was [NON-ENGLISH], it was that.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Then we figured out this was the 1st of June, 1909.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We figured it out, and that's all I remained with. 1909 is my birthday.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now at 21 years, I have to go to the army.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they took me, that army, and was-- you know, and I became a soldier.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was, I mean-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was but 21 months, 22 months in the army.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Life-- coming to the army, you know, even being in the army, you needed also some help, financially help, because the food what you got there was not sufficient, you see, to keep up yourself and your energy and everything.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Usually most of the soldiers, they got packages from home for food.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They got the zlotys, and they bought some food.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My mother tried-- I don't know how she tried, what she did, what.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She tried to send me all this-- the zlotys, I should be able to buy some food.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I lived.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Matter of fact, I have here a picture which I came to my brother.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was-- he was married.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That's the story.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He got married with a cousin, my mother's brother's daughter, and he lived in Lodz.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he want me always to come.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I should come to him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We're going to be together.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I said-- I don't want to be with nobody together.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You see, I want to be by myself.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And-- you know, when I had the free-- some holidays, I got the, you know, a--",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pass to go to wherever I want to, so I went to Lodz.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went there.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
